data.description: Looking for a cute, cottage style house? This house has had new tile and laminate flooring within the past 5 years, new HVAC in the past 3 years, and a new water heater in the past 2 years and is perfect for an individual or small family with the master and main bath on the first floor and a second bedroom and half bath upstairs. It has an open living plan and a laundry nook right inside of the side door. It has central heating and air and ceiling fans in the main bedroom and living room. With high, vaulted ceilings it feels very spacious and has plenty of storage under the eaves. The roof is approximately 19 years old and has been repaired recently. There is fencing around part of the property. The owner is willing to finance the property. The driveway is a shared drive with the front property bordering Meadowbrook Drive.
